title: Members of the Family
creator: Owen Wister
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text
description: LibriVox recording of Members of the Family, by Owen Wister. Read by David Wales. Members of the Family is a collection of eight short stories about people in the Wyoming Territory in the late 19th and early 20th centuries. (Summary by David Wales) For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. M4B format available
